OL,5, A Canadian judge has approved a        
OL,6, class-action lawsuit brought by three  
OL,7, parents who say their children became  
OL,8, addicted to video game Fortnite.       
OL,10,FThe plaintiffs say their children would
OL,11,Fforgo sleeping, eating and showering   
OL,12,Fbecause they were hooked on the game.  
OL,14,FIn court filings, they noted that the  
OL,15,FWorld Health Organization recognised   
OL,16,Fvideo-game addiction in 2018.          
OL,18,FThe lawsuit is against the game's      
OL,19,Fmaker, Epic Games, and its Canadian    
OL,20,Fsubsidiary.                            
